turbo.service.web.doc : base.Doc
turbo.service.web.doc =
  use base.syntax docEmbedTermLink docLink docParagraph docTransclude docWord
  {{
  {{ base.syntax.docExample 1 do db -> web db }} combines Turbo's HTTP control
  plane with the websocket signaling endpoint.
  
  This is the shared route intended for both local serving and cloud
  deployment.
  
  **Also see:** {{ docLink (docEmbedTermLink do service.http) }}, {{
